# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 1. SYSTEM FILES (Mac / Windows / Linux)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.log

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 2. IDE & EDITOR FILES (VS Code / Sublime / etc.)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
.idea/
*.sublime-project
*.sublime-workspace
*.swp
*.swo

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 3. LOCAL SERVER & CACHE FILES
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.vscode/
node_modules/
*.tmp

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 4. MEDIA FILES (OPTIONAL)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# If your videos are large (over 100MB), GitHub will reject them.
# Uncomment the lines below to prevent video files from being uploaded.
# *.mp4
# *.mov
# *.avi

# Uncomment this if you DON'T want to upload the logo to GitHub:
# vyron-logo.png

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 5. IMAGES & ASSETS (Recommendation)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
# It is usually fine to keep images like the logo, but if they are huge:
# *.png
# *.jpg
# *.jpeg
# *.gif

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 6. LOCAL ENVIRONMENT VARIABLES (Keep secrets safe!)
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.env
.env.local
.env.*.local

# ------------------------------------------------------------
# 7. GitHub specific folder
# ------------------------------------------------------------
.github/
